([Wikipedia][1])

[1]: https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Information_commons&oldid=1186082015#Software_commons

## About Software Commons

Public software sharing is great, for [a number of reasons][2]. But like any
[commons][3], the commons of publicly shared software must be protected against
two threats: [enclosure][4] and the [tragedy of the commons][5]; _too many_
restrictions and  _too few_. Sustainably sharing society's software means
balancing between the two extremes, and Software Commons does so using two
mechanisms: [licensing][6] and [Fair Share][7].

Read more [about Software Commons][8].

